    "causal_summary": "Candidate 8th idea (from the GLM-5.2 parallel lineage): decompose routing policy into three orthogonal knobs — Threshold (how much evidence to commit), Recovery (what happens after an uncertain/wrong pick), Provenance (where the vocab-to-mode evidence comes from). defaultMode is one corner (T low, R none, P static) of this space; the field conflates T and R and cannot express low-threshold + high-recovery. A hub's policy becomes a (T,R,P) triple plus a vocabulary table. This packet is the dive-ready scaffold; the presentation is authored, the 5-iteration SOL xhigh-fast dive is NOT yet run.",
